ComicInfo.Summary:
More trouble at the House of Grimm! The deranged doll named Dolores Twist tempts Violet into donning a slimy artifact found lying dormant under the stairs. Before the shivers can even finish rippling down her back, Violet begins to hear creepy noises echoing through her home. A voice from beyond signals the imminent arrival of a mysterious (and, as is the Dogwitch standard, undoubtedly kinky) houseguest. To make it through the day with dignity intact, Violet's going to have to relax and slide with it. Either that or go crazy with power tools.
